An Online Examination System using AI and NLP revolutionizes exams. NLP algorithms generate diverse, contextually accurate questions from academic texts, including multiple-choice and short answer formats with adjustable difficulty levels. The system enforces precise time limits and automatic submission, ensuring standardized testing. Its user-friendly interface and multi-device compatibility allow convenient exam access. Instant feedback for objective questions enhances the testing experience, making it efficient and secure. This AI and NLP integration streamlines question generation and improves the overall exam process.
